<p><b>Enjoy <font color=#669900>KDE 3</font></b>. With default settings, SuSE Linux 
will install the current version of this first-class
user interface. Intuitive menus facilitate access to the Linux
world for newcomers. The Internet-oriented desktop system offers a
host of valuable tools for professional users. The current
version of <b><font color=#669900>GNOME</font></b>, another excellent user interface, is also included on the CDs.</p>
<p>In addition, users can choose from a large number of
other freely configurable graphical user interfaces. Allow your
creativity to burst forth while you explore other window managers.</p>
